## Security (JWT + RBAC)

- Algorithm: HS256 · Access TTL: 30 min · Refresh TTL: 7 days
- Secret: `SAMPLEMIND_SECRET_KEY` env var — **never hardcode**
- Roles: `viewer` < `member` < `owner` < `admin`
- First registered account auto-gets `owner` role
- Auth routes at `POST /api/v1/auth/register|login|refresh`, `GET /api/v1/auth/me`

